text: William Hoare was a British gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. He also competed in two diving events at the same Olympics. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:British male divers Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
